}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw log --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看所有日志内容（从头开始）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all log content from the beginning"
}
]
}
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动 AI Agent 消息网关，连接 IM 平台并实时监听、自动处理消息。"
,
"en"
:
"Launch the AI Agent message gateway to connect to an IM platform for real-time listening and autonomous message processing."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw run [FLAG]"
:
null
}
]
,
"--weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable WeChat platform"
}
}
,
"--telegram"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用 Telegram 平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Telegram platform"
}
}
,
"--feishu"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用飞书平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Feishu platform"
}
}
,
"--qywx"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用企业微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Qywx (Enterprise WeChat) platform"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"该命令在前台运行，保持终端打开以持续监听消息。如需后台运行，请配合 screen/tmux 或使用 service 命令。\n启动前请确保已配置对应的 IM 平台服务（如 `x weixin login`）。\n支持同时启动多个 IM 平台（如 `x claw run --weixin --telegram`）。\n不指定平台时自动检测已登录的 IM 平台，默认回退到 weixin。\n新消息到达时自动分派到独立 worker 处理。\nAI Agent 回复引擎由 `x agent request` 决定，支持 claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli 等。\n内置心跳机制与 x cron 集成，支持定时唤醒和 proactive 任务执行。\n每个 chat 拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆，支持多会话并发。\n"
,
"en"
:
"This command runs in the foreground; keep the terminal open to continue listening. Use screen/tmux or the service command for background execution.\nEnsure the corresponding IM platform service is configured before starting (e.g. `x weixin login`).\nSupports starting multiple IM platforms simultaneously (e.g., `x claw run --weixin --telegram`).\nAuto-detects logged-in IM platforms when not specified, with weixin as fallback default.\nDispatches incoming messages to independent workers for processing.\nThe AI Agent reply engine is determined by `x agent request`, supporting claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli, etc.\nBuilt-in heartbeat mechanism with x cron integration supports scheduled wake-ups and proactive task execution.\nEach chat has an independent workspace with persistent context memory, supporting multi-session concurrency.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动网关服务（自动检测可用平台）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start gateway service (auto-detect available platform)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run --weixin --telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动微信和 Telegram 网关服务"
