"x claw run --qywx --feishu --telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 同时启动企业微信、飞书和 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start Qywx, Feishu and Telegram gateway services simultaneously"
}
]
}
,
